# Draft:Discord Diss Battles

Discord Diss Battles is a studio album created by American rapper Slashest. It was released on February 2024 of a YouTube video of different diss track projects that he wants his friends to make DISSTRACK. He invited his friends (Packgod, Yunk, Grimmmey, Yukidomari, XANAKIN SKYWOK, and ZephRaps. The album was inspired by Softwillyâ€™s Discord Rap Battles for permission.
